00:32:58.250 --> 00:33:02.240
And you came and said, "No, I did
not interview people for this.

00:33:02.240 --> 00:33:04.880
These people were my creations."

00:33:04.880 --> 00:33:10.450
I want to report to you an odd
occurrence that I had when teaching

00:33:10.450 --> 00:33:13.500
at a middle school in
Frederick many years ago

00:33:13.500 --> 00:33:16.490
that the social studies
teacher there was one

00:33:16.490 --> 00:33:18.950
