irate and denied it.

00:33:44.350 --> 00:33:47.810
I came to know of it, and
she told them, you know,

00:33:47.810 --> 00:33:49.300
"How dare you question me."

00:33:49.300 --> 00:33:55.170 position:56%
So some of those students came to me
for confirmation, and I said, "Well,

00:33:55.170 --> 00:33:58.880
yes, it's fiction," and then
they told me what was going on.

00:33:58.880 --> 00:34:01.930
At the end of the day
I just had lunch

00:34:01.930 --> 00:34:04.520
with her very quietly
one time, and said that,

00:34:04.520 --> 00:34:07.800
